Mnquma municipal Manager Sindile Tantsi has been arrested by a Hawks task team. National Hawks spokesman Brigadier Hangwani Mulaudzi said the suspect was arrested this morning on charges of fraud and corruption amounting to millions of rands. &#8220;He is currently in custody. He was arrested today between Butterworth and Mthatha. He will appear in the Butterworth Magistrate Court tomorrow morning to face charges against him,&#8221; Mulaudzi said. More details in the paper tomorrow